data.description: New Roof to be put on before closing. 3rd bedroom is currently converted to large home office and bar.   Key Features:  Waterfront Paradise: Situated on a tranquil canal, this residence offers direct access to the sparkling waters of the Bay and a quick boat ride to Gulf. Whether you're an avid boater or simply love waterfront views, this location is a dream come true.  Spacious Living: Step inside to discover an inviting open floor plan with abundant natural light. The living spaces seamlessly flow, creating an ideal setting for family gatherings and entertaining guests.  Private Master Suite: The master bedroom offers a peaceful retreat with its spacious layout and en-suite bathroom. Wake up to picturesque canal views and enjoy the convenience of a walk-in closet.  Outdoor Oasis: The outdoor area is a true paradise, complete with a boat lift for your watercraft and a spacious deck for soaking up the sun. You'll relish in the serene canal views and the ability to set off on aquatic adventures at a moment's notice.  Polynesian Isles Lifestyle: Living in the Polynesian Isles Neighborhood means you're just minutes away from the area's best schools, shopping, dining, and beautiful beaches. Enjoy the quintessential Gulf Breeze lifestyle with this amazing property.
